# MVP 1 ‚Äî Product & Auth Model

## Deployment model (MVP 1)

| Aspect | MVP 1 (now) | Future (SaaS) |
|--------|-------------|---------------|
| Sales | **Beli putus** ‚Äî satu bisnis, satu install/deployment | Multi-tenant subscription |
| Tenancy | Single organization per instance | Workspace / org per customer |
| Public signup | **Tidak ada** | Register + plan picker |
| New team members | **Owner invite** via email ‚Üí set password | Self-serve + billing seats |

**Do not build** public `/register`, open signup, or multi-tenant billing in MVP 1 unless user explicitly asks for SaaS phase.

## Auth & onboarding (MVP 1)

1. **First visit (fresh deploy)** ‚Äî `/setup` wizard (WordPress-style): nama bisnis, owner, email, password. One-time only; blocked after `instance_settings.setup_completed_at` is set.
2. **Login** ‚Äî email + password (Supabase Auth when configured).
3. **Existing / dev installs** ‚Äî migration 005 backfills setup complete if owner already linked; demo uses `db:seed` + `db:seed-auth` (optional).
4. **CS / Supervisor / Owner tambahan** ‚Äî hanya **Owner** yang mengundang:
   - Settings ‚Üí Manajemen Agent ‚Üí **Undang via email**
   - Supabase `inviteUserByEmail` ‚Üí email link ‚Üí halaman set password (`/accept-invite`)
   - Trigger DB link `auth.users` ke baris `agents` via `user_metadata.agent_id`
5. **Forgot password** ‚Äî tetap ada untuk semua role.
6. **Demo shortcuts** di login ‚Äî hanya dev/demo; label jujur.
7. **Optional `SETUP_TOKEN`** env ‚Äî wajib di form setup jika diset (production deploy).

## Role rules (unchanged)

- `cs` ‚Äî assigned customers + manual shares
- `supervisor` ‚Äî team view, manage agents (role change), no invite
- `owner` ‚Äî supervisor + **invite users**, billing, export approval, field rules

Invite permission: **`role === 'owner'` only** ‚Äî not `manage_agents` alone.

## Copy (Indonesian)

- Login footer: *"Belum punya akun? Hubungi owner bisnis Anda."* ‚Äî **not** "Daftar sekarang"
- Invite success: *"Undangan dikirim ke {email}"*
- Accept invite page: *"Atur password untuk akun ChatCRM Anda"*
- Setup page: *"Setup awal ChatCRM"* / *"Isi data bisnis dan akun owner"*

## Technical constraints

- Invite **must** use server function + `SUPABASE_SECRET_KEY` (admin API) ‚Äî never expose secret in client.
- No `signUp` / public registration in app code ‚Äî **except** one-time `/setup` server fn on fresh instance.
- DB trigger `handle_new_user`: link via `agent_id` metadata only ‚Äî **do not** auto-create agent on orphan signup.
- Agent row created **before** invite (status `pending`); becomes `active` after user sets password.

## When implementing SaaS later

- Add `organizations`, `memberships`, subdomain routing
- Replace single-tenant seed with org provisioning
- Re-enable guarded registration or checkout ‚Üí provision flow
- See future note in `AGENTS.md` ‚Äî do not half-implement SaaS in MVP 1 files
